{"about_the_game":"We combined a <strong>Roguelite Deckbuilder</strong>, a <strong>Turn-Based RPG</strong>, and a <strong>bloodthirsty orc battle-mage</strong>, to create <strong>Korga</strong>! Enter her domain and defeat anyone foolish enough to challenge you.<br>Craft your <strong>Deck</strong>, enhance your <strong>Weapons</strong>, and forge your <strong>Gladiator Emblem</strong> to customize your playstyle.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754870/extras/PlayerCombat.gif?t=1719933036\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754870/extras/BountyHunter.png?t=1719933036\" /><br>Meet <strong>Korga, Akhvar\u2019s ruthless bounty hunter!</strong><br>Gold has no sway over her; it's the thrill of the hunt and the heads of her prey she values above all. She drags these trophies back to her <strong>Arena</strong>, trapping their souls to relive their defeat over and over.<br>It\u2019s more than just a fight, it\u2019s her pleasure.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754870/extras/Enemies1.gif?t=1719933036\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754870/extras/ArenaBiomes.png?t=1719933036\" /><br><strong>Korga</strong> might be merciless, but she\u2019s got a twisted sense of hospitality. <br>She can morph the <strong>Arena</strong> with a snap of her fingers to give her captured foes a taste of home before their battle begins anew. Whether it\u2019s the icy chill of the tundra or the scorching heat of a volcano, she ensures every fight is both familiar and fearsome.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754870/extras/Procgen2.gif?t=1719933036\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754870/extras/Banner6.png?t=1719933036\" /><br>Embrace the chaos in a land where every encounter is a leap into the unknown. With ever-changing challenges and choices that could spell victory or downfall, <strong>Korga</strong> is a test of strategy, skill, and adaptability.<br>Will you remain the <strong>Champion of the Arena</strong>, or will you fall prey to your own avarice? <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754870/extras/Roguelite.gif?t=1719933036\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754870/extras/Banner3.png?t=1719933036\" /><br><strong>Deckbuilding</strong> melds <strong>strategic depth</strong> with <strong>build customization</strong>. Add new cards to your deck throughout the game and discover amazing combinations! <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754870/extras/CardsGif.gif?t=1719933036\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754870/extras/SpiritBeasts.png?t=1719933036\" /><br>The <strong>Arena</strong> is an endless challenge, with the glory of victory and gloom of defeat lurking behind every corner. To better prepare for the challenges ahead, <strong>Korga</strong> can progress through the <strong>Spirit Beast</strong> paths and obtain their powers.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754870/extras/Skilltree.gif?t=1719933036\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754870/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1719933036","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754870/page.bg.jpg?t=1719933036","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754870/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1719933036","capsule