 captured foes a taste of home before their battle begins anew. Whether it\u2019s the icy chill of the tundra or the scorching heat of a volcano, she ensures every fight is both familiar and fearsome.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754870/extras/Procgen2.gif?t=1719933036\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754870/extras/Banner6.png?t=1719933036\" /><br>Embrace the chaos in a land where every encounter is a leap into the unknown. With ever-changing challenges and choices that could spell victory or downfall, <strong>Korga</strong> is a test of strategy, skill, and adaptability.<br>Will you remain the <strong>Champion of the Arena</strong>, or will you fall prey to your own avarice? <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754870/extras/Roguelite.gif?t=1719933036\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754870/extras/Banner3.png?t=1719933036\" /><br><strong>Deckbuilding</strong> melds <strong>strategic depth</strong> with <strong>build customization</strong>. Add new cards to your deck throughout the game and discover amazing combinations! <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754870/extras/CardsGif.gif?t=1719933036\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2754870/extras/SpiritBeasts.png?t=1719933036\" /><br>The <strong>Arena</strong> is an endless challenge, with the glory of victory and gloom of defeat lurking behind every corner. To better prepare for the challenges ahead, <strong>Korga</strong> can progress through the <strong>Spirit Beast</strong> paths and obtain their powers.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_asse